# Cursor Rules for Psychoroid Studios

## Project Description

Psychoroid Studios is a React-native 3D digital asset creation and distribution platform. It allows users to convert 2D images into various 3D formats, supporting game development, 3D printing, e-commerce, and digital content creation. The platform provides a range of features and tools for 3D asset management, editing, and optimization.

## Key Features

1. 3D Conversion Engine:
   - Automated 2D to 3D conversion
   - Multiple export formats (GLTF/GLB, STL/OBJ, USDZ, FBX)
   - Real-time 3D preview and editing
   - Scale and measurement tools
   - Texture and material editing

2. Game Development Resources:
   - Ready-to-use game assets
   - Game Character Designer (GCD)
   - Unity & Unreal Engine compatible formats
   - Optimized asset packaging

3. E-commerce & Manufacturing:
   - 3D printing-ready files
   - E-commerce product visualization
   - AR product preview support
   - Technical specifications export

4. Professional Tools:
   - Batch processing capabilities
   - Quality validation tools
   - Measurement and scaling tools
   - Format-specific optimizations

