## Deployment

- The platform is hosted at https://psychoroid.com.
- It is deployed using a modern hosting service: Vercel.
- Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) pipelines are set up for automated deployments.

## Target Audience

- Game developers
- 3D artists and designers
- E-commerce businesses
- Manufacturers and 3D printing enthusiasts
- Digital content creators

## Monetization

- Freemium model with basic features available for free
- Subscription-based access to advanced features and tools
- Pay-per-use model for specific services (e.g., batch processing, high-quality exports)
- Marketplace for selling and purchasing 3D assets

